WEBVTT

00:00:01.142 --> 00:00:02.316
I once said,

00:00:02.849 --> 00:00:05.483
"If you want to liberate a society,

00:00:05.507 --> 00:00:07.523
all you need is the Internet."

00:00:08.261 --> 00:00:09.415
I was wrong.

00:00:10.121 --> 00:00:12.701
I said those words back in 2011,

00:00:12.725 --> 00:00:15.647
when a Facebook page I anonymously created

00:00:15.671 --> 00:00:17.986
helped spark the Egyptian revolution.

00:00:18.724 --> 00:00:23.304
The Arab Spring revealed
social media's greatest potential,

00:00:23.328 --> 00:00:27.336
but it also exposed
its greatest shortcomings.

00:00:28.003 --> 00:00:32.023
The same tool that united us
to topple dictators